comment: /**  * Returns {@code true} if this matches {@code t}, {@code false} otherwise.  */
code: /**  * Returns {@code true} if this matches {@code t}, {@code false} otherwise.  */ boolean matches(T t).

comment: /**  * Returns a new matcher which returns {@code true} if both this and the  * given matcher return {@code true}.  */
code: /**  * Returns a new matcher which returns {@code true} if both this and the  * given matcher return {@code true}.  */ Matcher<T> and(Matcher<? super T> other).

comment: /**  * Returns a new matcher which returns {@code true} if either this or the  * given matcher return {@code true}.  */
code: /**  * Returns a new matcher which returns {@code true} if either this or the  * given matcher return {@code true}.  */ Matcher<T> or(Matcher<? super T> other).
